OL,3,CAdam Peaty hits out at 'burying' of
OL,4,Cdoping after China win gold
OL,6,FAdam Peaty has criticised the presence
OL,7,Fof competitors who had previously
OL,8,Ffailed drug tests, as ITV News' Ellie
OL,9,FPitt reports
OL,11,FAdam Peaty has hit out at the
OL,12,F"burying" of doping evidence after a
OL,13,FChinese team that featured competitors
OL,14,Fwho had previously failed drug tests
OL,15,Fwon gold.
