OL,3,CAdam Peaty hits out at 'burying' of
OL,4,Cdoping after China win gold
OL,6,FQin Haiyang and Sun Jiajun helped
OL,7,Ftheir nation claim gold in the men's
OL,8,F4100 metres medley relay but they
OL,9,Fwere two of 23 Chinese swimmers who
OL,10,Ftested positive for the banned
OL,11,Fsubstance trimetazidine prior to the
OL,12,FTokyo Olympics.
OL,14,FThey were later cleared to compete on
OL,15,Fthe basis of a finding they had
OL,16,Funknowingly ingested the drug via
OL,17,Fcontaminated food.
