OL,3,CAdam Peaty hits out at 'burying' of
OL,4,Cdoping after China win gold
OL,6,FQin also failed a different
OL,7,Fperformance-enhancing drug in 2017 `
OL,8,Fwhich was also blamed on food
OL,9,Fcontamination at the time.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News, the 29-year-old
OL,12,FTeam GB swimmer said: "For me, my only
OL,13,Fthing I care about is making sure I am
OL,14,Fracing fair people and they're not
OL,15,Fcheating, so what else I can do is
OL,16,Fspeak out when we know that people are
OL,17,Fcontaminating in very suspicious
OL,18,Fenvironments but also that they're
OL,19,Fdoing it twice - it's been buried.
