OL,3,CAdam Peaty hits out at 'burying' of
OL,4,Cdoping after China win gold
OL,6,F"If there's truly a contamination and
OL,7,Fthey're truly not at fault then why
OL,8,Fbury it?"
OL,10,FPeaty said one of the biggest problems
OL,11,Fis a significant amount of the anti-
OL,12,Fdrug measures competitors are placed
OL,13,Funder are carried out by the home
OL,14,Fnation.
OL,16,FHe said many athletes across numerous
OL,17,Fsports "feel very let down by the
OL,18,Fcurrent system" and that needs to
OL,19,Fchange to improve trust and
OL,20,Ftransparency.
