OL,3,CAdam Peaty hits out at 'burying' of
OL,4,Cdoping after China win gold
OL,6,FThe issue heavily overshadowed the
OL,7,Fbuild-up to Paris 2024 and appeared to
OL,8,Flead to mistrust from several swimmers
OL,9,Fin the system.
OL,11,FKatie Ledecky and Caeleb Dressel
OL,12,Fexpressed their misgivings and Peaty
OL,13,Fjoined the clamour on the final night
OL,14,Fof the swimming competitions as he
OL,15,Fsingled out Qin for criticism.
