OL,3,CAdam Peaty hits out at 'burying' of
OL,4,Cdoping after China win gold
OL,6,FPeaty's experience at the 2024
OL,7,FOlympics was overshadowed by a
OL,8,Fpositive Covid diagnosis the day after
OL,9,Fcoming second in the men's 100m
OL,10,Fbreaststroke by just 0.02 seconds.
OL,12,FHe described on Saturday how he had
OL,13,Fhad the "worst week" of his life
OL,14,Fphysically.
OL,16,FWhen asked how felt about missing out
OL,17,Fon gold by such a short distance, he
OL,18,Fsaid: "It's all over really."
