OL,3,CAdam Peaty hits out at 'burying' of
OL,4,Cdoping after China win gold
OL,6,F"Firstly your initial reaction is it's
OL,7,Fa silver by 0.02 but then I understand
OL,8,Fthat the illness that I was so
OL,9,Funfortunate to get at the time I got
OL,10,Fit was just very unfortunate but at
OL,11,Fthe same time I am very happy I did
OL,12,Fcome away with a medal because it
OL,13,Fcould have been so much worse."
OL,15,FHe added: "A lot to be proud but also
OL,16,Fa lot to digest."
